[30;1m427 | [0m[35m    def _add_role(self, role: Role, /) -> None:[0m
[30;1m428 | [0m[35m        # roles get added to the bottom (position 1, pos 0 is @everyone)[0m
[30;1m429 | [0m[35m        # so since self.roles has the @everyone role, we can't increment[0m
[30;1m430 | [0m[35m        # its position because it's stuck at position 0. Luckily x += False[0m
[30;1m431 | [0m[35m        # is equivalent to adding 0. So we cast the position to a bool and[0m
